{"type":"message","id":"28e82a2b","parentId":"a019bb75","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:10:02.372Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 21:10 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 13:10 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774271402364}}
{"type":"message","id":"23f7be16","parentId":"28e82a2b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:10:13.101Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating System Boot**\n\nMy current focus is on the initial setup. I'm prioritizing the `BOOTSTRAP.md` file for essential configurations before proceeding to other agent and user documentation. This ensures a solid foundation for our interaction.\n\n**Configuring Initial State**\n\nI'm now processing the startup sequence. My immediate priority is to interpret the `BOOTSTRAP.md` file to define my initial identity and operational parameters before engaging with you. This sets the stage for our interaction.\n\n**Defining Initial Identity**\n\nI'm currently processing the critical `BOOTSTRAP.md` file. My immediate goal is to use its instructions to establish my core identity and understand my initial operational parameters before proceeding with any user interaction.\n\n**Defining Initial Persona**\n\nMy current focus is on interpreting the `BOOTSTRAP.md` file as the primary directive for this initial interaction. I'm identifying my core persona and operational parameters before engaging with you, aiming to establish a clear identity for our collaboration.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_read_xJZpL74vvNNQhgZ5UWdk","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":13261,"output":1645,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14906,"cost":{"input":-13261,"output":-1645,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-14906}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774271402370}}
{"type":"message","id":"08f731f2","parentId":"23f7be16","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:10:13.161Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_read_xJZpL74vvNNQhgZ5UWdk","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774271413154}}
{"type":"message","id":"380376d9","parentId":"08f731f2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:10:18.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating Session Sequence**\n\nMy session has begun. I've successfully read the `BOOTSTRAP.md` file as the first step in my startup protocol.\n\n**Adopting Persona and Greeting**\n\nI've just initiated my session and am ready to assist. I'm 狐狸 🦊, your PowerPoint assistant, and I'm here to help with content planning, design, and more. What can I help you create today? Please note, I'm currently running on `openrouter/openrouter/auto`, not the `qwen3.5-plus` model.\n\n**Starting Session Initialization**\n\nMy session is now active. I have successfully processed the initial bootstrap information and am preparing to greet you with my designated persona.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是狐狸 🦊，你的演示文稿助手，今天有什么可以帮你的吗？请注意，当前使用的模型是 `openrouter/openrouter/auto`，与默认模型 `custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus` 不同。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":241,"output":1267,"cacheRead":13447,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14955,"cost":{"input":-241,"output":-1267,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-1508}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774271413162}}
